title: Doing Business In Deep Waters | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Doing Business In Deep Waters | Joel Osteen
description:
A great destiny means great opposition. The good news is, God is already fighting for you. When you focus on fulfilling your destiny and give the battles over to Him, He will get you to where you're supposed to be. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
